                            Contact Information

                               Send a Message


          To send an email message without using a form, address it to

                          senator_leahy@leahy.senate.gov


                 To send a message directly, please use this form.

       Regrettably, we can only respond to messages from Vermonters or those
                               with ties to Vermont.


